    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to one side on a separate <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 12-15 min or until golden and crispy</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1679397846460-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
