            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the bacon is cooking, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Combine your <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>tomato ketchup</strong> in a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> – this is your <strong>curried ketchup</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1679397850750-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1679397850750-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1679397850750-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
