            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are golden, return the <strong>masala sauce</strong> to a medium heat and add the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>chopped coriander </strong>(save some for garnish!) to the pot</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the chips are fully coated in the sauce – these are your <strong>masala chips</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
