      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, top the <strong>toasted brioche base </strong>with the <strong>cheesy bacon</strong>, <strong>fried egg</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>curried ketchup</strong> and <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>toasted brioche lid </strong>and serve with the <strong>masala chips </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
